# Super Admin Responsive Design

This document outlines the responsive design patterns used in the Super Admin section to ensure a consistent experience across different device sizes.

## Layout Structure

The Super Admin layout uses different components for desktop and mobile views:

```tsx
// From src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx
<Suspense fallback={<div>Loading...</div>}>
  <div className="hidden md:block">
    <Desktop>{children}</Desktop>
  </div>

  <div className="block md:hidden">
    <Mobile>{children}</Mobile>
  </div>
</Suspense>
```

This approach uses Tailwind's responsive utilities to show/hide components based on screen size.

